name: Bittorrent in 1987
description: Back in the days before we'd even heard of The Internet, Dad's mate from work was the single source of all my pirated videogames. Every few weeks, Dad would hand me a pile of floppy disks and I'd spend the next few days glued to the PC. This one's for you Graham, wherever you are. Procedurally randomized to keep it fresh :: shig_nft 2021
